       - Validates GR predictions against historical experiments
       - Tests AI modules (Neural ODE, MetricGNN, anomaly detection)
       - Validates quantum gravity plugins (CDT, spin foam, causal sets)

       **Testing Philosophy:**
       - Write tests first (TDD) for new physics components
       - Maintain ≥80% code coverage for core modules
       - Every bug fix includes a regression test
       - All tests must pass before any merge to main
